com.joliciel.talismane.fr.ftb

Interface PhraseUnit

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Entity, PhraseElement

    public interface PhraseUnit
extends PhraseElement, Entity
    a single word within the French Treebank, along with it's various attributes and position inside a phrase
    Author:
    Assaf Urieli

        boolean isCompound()
        Is this phrase unit compound or not? If false, all subunits should be considered as separate tokens. If true, all subunits should be considred as part of a single compound token.
